"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-world-europe-parisians-on-tiktok-plead-don-t-come-to-paris-for-the-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get ST's newsletters delivered to your inbox  People on TikTok also warned that there could be severe overcrowding on trains during Paris Olympics 2024.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0621970540419782e-15, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703099307, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}, {\"begin\": 252, \"end\": 258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232427750616791e-46, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: REUTERS  PublishedJun 15, 2024, 08:01 AM  UpdatedJun 15, 2024, 10:30 PM  PARIS-\\\"This is a video for anyone that's coming to Paris Olympics 2024,\\\" a woman says in a clip posted to TikTok.\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 481, \"end\": 495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 536, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232427750616791e-46, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She pauses briefly, and then continues: \\\"Do not come.\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cancel everything.\\\"\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The video, which was uploaded in November, now has more than 700,000 views.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The creator, Ms Miranda Starcevic, is a 31-year-old French American who lives in Paris.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 712, \"end\": 719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miranda_warning\", \"score\": 0.999999988682248, \"rank\": 1.1317607167385572e-08, \"text\": \"Miranda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miranda_warning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miranda_warning\"}, {\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 777, \"end\": 782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She usually records herself speaking in French, but thought a message about the Olympics would reach more people if it were in English.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Ms Starcevic wanted her viewers to know that from her perspective, of French citizens who \\\"are kind of middle class\\\", as she put it: \\\"Nobody wants the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 995, \"end\": 1001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9991635268795916, \"rank\": 0.0008362513204941774, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just a hot mess.\\\"\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a visual-first international platform with many young users, TikTok is full of Olympics content.\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232427750616791e-46, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in addition to feel-good windows into athletes' lives and promotional videos from organisers and sponsors, there are also unfiltered clips from residents warning potential visitors that Paris may not deliver its best during the Games.\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1406, \"end\": 1411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A 24-year-old student whose display name is Leo Nora has posted several short clips about the Paris Games, stating they will be \\\"dangerous\\\" and \\\"hell on earth\\\".\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1500, \"end\": 1503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"score\": 0.9999998112380304, \"rank\": 1.8876192924100548e-07, \"text\": \"Leo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\"}, {\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"score\": 0.999985000427104, \"rank\": 1.499206239831317e-05, \"text\": \"Nora\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In one of her videos, she says into the camera: \\\"If you are planning on coming to Paris for the Olympic Games, why?\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1700, \"end\": 1705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not come.\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not come!\\\"\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The clip has been viewed more than a million times.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have lived in Paris my whole life,\\\" Ms Leo Nora said in an interview.\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1886, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1831, \"end\": 1836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"score\": 0.9999998112380304, \"rank\": 1.8876192924100548e-07, \"text\": \"Leo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\"}, {\"begin\": 1860, \"end\": 1864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"score\": 0.999985000427104, \"rank\": 1.499206239831317e-05, \"text\": \"Nora\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been to really big events in Paris.\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1924, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What prompted me to talk about it is I know how it can go right - and how it can go wrong.\\\"\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 2022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She and Ms Starcevic had similar reasons for encouraging people to avoid the Games.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both said they were unhappy that the city asked students to give up their student housing, so the accommodations could be used for workers during the Games.\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And both expressed frustration and fears around transportation.\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fares to ride on the Paris Metro will be almost doubling during the Games - a bit of Olympic surge pricing that has already caused much grumbling.\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2352, \"end\": 2363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_M\\u00e9tro\", \"score\": 0.9999998407888724, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Metro\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_M\\u00e9tro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_M\\u00e9tro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers and government officials are concerned about strikes by transportation workers during the Games, as well as more serious issues like terrorism.\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some creators have posted about Paris' pervasive tourist scams, pickpockets and recent hotel price hikes.\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2667, \"end\": 2672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People on TikTok also warned that there could be severe overcrowding on trains.\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2752, \"end\": 2758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232427750616791e-46, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not rare to have people fainting\\\" in the Metro, Ms Leo Nora said, adding that when someone faints, \\\"the line stops, which causes delays\\\".\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2880, \"end\": 2883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"score\": 0.9999998112380304, \"rank\": 1.8876192924100548e-07, \"text\": \"Leo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\"}, {\"begin\": 2884, \"end\": 2888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"score\": 0.999985000427104, \"rank\": 1.499206239831317e-05, \"text\": \"Nora\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Tessa Bicard, an executive at a cosmetics company whose TikTok handle is Madame Tartempion, posted a video titled \\\"The Olympics are going to be a nightmare for Paris\\\".\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 3138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3027, \"end\": 3033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232427750616791e-46, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}, {\"begin\": 3131, \"end\": 3136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has drawn more than 750,000 views and hundreds of comments.\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Bicard, who is originally from Northern California and has lived in Paris for over 12 years, said in an interview that she was actually a big fan of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3275, \"end\": 3280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have watched them every year since I was a kid,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really like the swimming - and women's gymnastics, of course.\\\"\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, she said: \\\"This is the least excited I have ever been about the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mainly, she said, that is because she does not have tickets.\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are too expensive or impossible to get,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She also stressed that all the different construction projects for the Games have already made daily life difficult.\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The expected influx of millions of Olympics visitors, she fears, will just make things worse.\", \"from\": 3817, \"to\": 3910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My bus route has been complete chaos.\\\"\", \"from\": 3911, \"to\": 3950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As an American living in Paris, Ms Bicard said she often uses her TikTok account to answer questions about the city, in addition to fun tips like \\\"how to spot an American in Paris\\\".\", \"from\": 3952, \"to\": 4133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3958, \"end\": 3966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9981636421152366, \"rank\": 0.001839728120769889, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3977, \"end\": 3982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4018, \"end\": 4024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232427750616791e-46, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}, {\"begin\": 4114, \"end\": 4122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9981636421152366, \"rank\": 0.001839728120769889, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 4126, \"end\": 4131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Americans ask: \\\"Where's the best place to stay?\", \"from\": 4135, \"to\": 4182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What's the best neighbourhood?\", \"from\": 4183, \"to\": 4213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you have a favourite restaurant?\", \"from\": 4214, \"to\": 4249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All that kind of stuff,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4250, \"to\": 4284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She replies to as many people as she can.\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a certain aspect of 'I feel like I can trust you because you speak with an American accent',\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4413, \"end\": 4421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9981636421152366, \"rank\": 0.001839728120769889, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it comes to the Games, Ms Bicard's view is a bit softer than that of more vocal Olympics naysayers like Ms Leo Nora and Ms Starcevic.\", \"from\": 4443, \"to\": 4581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4555, \"end\": 4558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"score\": 0.9999998112380304, \"rank\": 1.8876192924100548e-07, \"text\": \"Leo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\"}, {\"begin\": 4559, \"end\": 4563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"score\": 0.999985000427104, \"rank\": 1.499206239831317e-05, \"text\": \"Nora\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you are going to be here for the Olympics, hopefully this is not your once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to visit Paris,\\\" she said, adding that she expects it to be logistically challenging.\", \"from\": 4583, \"to\": 4773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4697, \"end\": 4702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's going to be really tricky and not at all pleasant to try to do some of those 'Paris' things,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4775, \"to\": 4892, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4867, \"end\": 4872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And like Ms Starcevic and Ms Leo Nora - and most Paris residents - Ms Bicard said she was expecting the Metro to be \\\"a total mess\\\" when the Games start.\", \"from\": 4894, \"to\": 5046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4923, \"end\": 4926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"score\": 0.9999998112380304, \"rank\": 1.8876192924100548e-07, \"text\": \"Leo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\"}, {\"begin\": 4927, \"end\": 4931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"score\": 0.999985000427104, \"rank\": 1.499206239831317e-05, \"text\": \"Nora\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\"}, {\"begin\": 4943, \"end\": 4948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2045953954081995e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Already, she said, there are posters and billboards around the city encouraging residents to anticipate the Games.\", \"from\": 5048, \"to\": 5162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many see it as \\\"coded language\\\" hinting at what many people are already thinking: \\\"Leave the city if you can - or if you can afford it.\", \"from\": 5164, \"to\": 5299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"NYTIMES  Olympics 2024  France  TikTok  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 5299, \"to\": 5455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5332, \"end\": 5338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232427750616791e-46, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 5456, \"to\": 5470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 5472, \"to\": 5489, \"entities\": []}]}"